verbose_text: To evaluate the associations of MYPT1 / CD31 combined expression with various clinicopathological parameters of PCa, all 234 PCa patients were divided into MYPT1-low / CD31-high (n = 61), MYPT1-high / CD31-low (n = 71), MYPT1-low / CD31-low (n = 50) and MYPT1-high / CD31-high (n = 50) groups by setting cut-off value at the median MYPT1 or CD31 expression level.
evidence: expression with various clinicopathological parameters of PCa
